reviewText:
Pandora

The sea is blue;
the snowy mountains glow;
the rustic settlments bleam with life;
explore it all, before you die;
but never fear, you can come back to life;
and again, explore it all;
through the world, you must make it;
conqure it all, and make or break it;
defeat Jack, you must do;
and save pandora, through and through.

You should play this because:

Longplay: I have nearly 60 hours of gameplay and I still haven't reached level 30;
Claptrap;
Too much loot;
You can make tiny psychopats turn against their torturer: just shoot the chains;
Handsome Jack;
All the people you love from Borderlands are there;
Throw a party with only two people;
Humor;
11/10 would laugh again
